    67â†’| **Ready** | ğŸŸ¢ Green | New files that will be uploaded | Upload to storage |
    68â†’| **Existing** | ğŸ”µ Blue | Files already uploaded previously | Skip upload, show notification |
    69â†’| **Duplicates** | ğŸŸ¡ Yellow | Same file selected multiple times in current batch | Keep one copy, skip duplicates |
    70â†’| **Uploading** | ğŸŸ  Orange | Files currently being processed | Show progress indicator |
    71â†’| **Successful** | âœ… Green | Files uploaded successfully | Mark as complete |
